{"type":"text","timestamp":1784180546924,"sessionID":"ses_0968f2113ffehJfWsGHuGr12Oc","part":{"id":"prt_f69728dd90011Ob5era1z0WwWk","messageID":"msg_f69722df50011JIi4WFLrGINhk","sessionID":"ses_0968f2113ffehJfWsGHuGr12Oc","type":"text","text":"I now understand the workflow contract. I'm the detached fan-out lineage (I AM the glm-5.2 executor). `artifact_dir` binds directly to the lineage dir. Let me set up task tracking and begin grounding research by reading the canon and benchmark sources.","time":{"start":1784180542937,"end":1784180546922}}}
