{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784181313489,"sessionID":"ses_0968f2113ffehJfWsGHuGr12Oc","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"call_1080ac7c03314eec9fb7f3de","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/066-command-surface-benchmark/012-command-improvement-research/research/lineages/glm52-max/deep-research-strategy.md","newString":"<!-- ANCHOR:what-failed -->\n## 8. WHAT FAILED\n- Shell family-loop with unquoted `$f` path produced `0/0` router-core counts; re-ran with `find -exec grep`. Minor cost. (iteration 2)\n<!-- /ANCHOR:what-failed -->","oldString":"<!-- ANCHOR:what-failed -->\n## 8. WHAT FAILED\n[First iteration — populated after iteration 1 completes]\n<!-- /ANCHOR:what-failed -->"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/066-command-surface-benchmark/012-command-improvement-research/research/lineages/glm52-max/deep-research-strategy.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/066-command-surface-benchmark/012-command-improvement-research/research/lineages/glm52-max/deep-research-strategy.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/066-command-surface-benchmark/012-command-improvement-research/research/lineages/glm52-max/deep-research-strategy.md\n@@ -49,9 +49,9 @@\n ---\n \n <!-- ANCHOR:what-failed -->\n ## 8. WHAT FAILED\n-[First iteration — populated after iteration 1 completes]\n+- Shell family-loop with unquoted `$f` path produced `0/0` router-core counts; re-ran with `find -exec grep`. Minor cost. (iteration 2)\n <!-- /ANCHOR:what-failed -->\n \n ---\n \n","filediff":{"file":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Devel